## Trust in the platform

Tochka has been online since 2014 and we're here to stay. We're a small dedicated team of staff that are here to keep the market great.

## Minimizing risk for buyers
Tochka offers 7 days escrow system and 2-of-3 multisig. Multisig payments are avaiable for PREMIUM and PREMIUM+ vendors who have filled in ther multisig signer wallet public key.

## Removing bad products
Tochka Free Market has partnered with DNMAvengers, an forum and community whom are dedicated to reduce harm & spread awareness via testing product suspected of containing adulterations.

This partnership create a system that makes it very hard for vendors at Tochka Free Market to sell adulterated products without it going unnoticed.

If you suspect you have recieved an adulterated/wrong substance you can create an report on DNMAvengers forum.

[avengersdutyk3xf.onion](http://avengersdutyk3xf.onion)
